{"tid":569802,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【FB更新】FB Messenger隨時加人視訊聊天 Technology","createTime":"2018-02-23T05:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T05:02:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"18ab6923c19b8921a9ee564e8b2ded9bb6c2a1cc","tid":569802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180223/20312399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F20312399&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ00bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=88813cb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F20312399&h=d228475c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180223/20312399</a><br />\n<br />\n【FB更新】FB Messenger隨時加人視訊聊天<br />\nTechnology   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180223/large/sub5200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180223%2Flarge%2Fsub5200.jpg&h=2f62c48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFacebook Messenger更新後令群組視訊聊天更為實用。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook Messenger近日更新，原本的Group Video Chat（群組視訊聊天）功能，可同時在畫面顯示的成員增加至6人，但最多可以50人參加群組聊天，所以多於6人聊天時，用家可從畫面下方的群組成員中，選擇其中一人作主畫面顯示。不過經實際測試，因為數據傳輸所限，畫面比較矇，睇唔清對方個樣，但聲音是清晰的，最大問題係太多人同時講嘢會好混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180223/large/sub5201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180223%2Flarge%2Fsub5201.jpg&h=e3c8c411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMessenger群組視訊聊天現時最多可同時顯示6個人的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180223/large/sub5202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180223%2Flarge%2Fsub5202.jpg&h=6d47c3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如多於6人時，會以其中一人變為主畫面，用家可自行選擇主畫面。　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180223/large/sub5203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180223%2Flarge%2Fsub5203.jpg&h=a1edc36c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按「加人」的圖示，就可隨時於中途加人進群組聊天。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今次更新中最實用的功能是可中途加人，群組聊天不論視訊或音訊都可以隨時追加朋友入群組，而且每位成員都可加朋友進來，中途加人冇難度。如在不幸在中途斷線，連線後會自動回復群組視訊聊天，想借斷線為藉口離開會議也不行。　<br />\n<br />\n記者：馬子聰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180223/large/sub5204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180223%2Flarge%2Fsub5204.jpg&h=ab28ca75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可按「加入」隨意加入Facebook的朋友進群組，也可搜尋人名加入。"}]}